Title: Invisible Evidence
Plot: Warrick's appearance at the preliminary hearing on a rape and murder case goes terribly wrong when the only piece of evidence is thrown out on a technicality. Grissom and the team have 24 hours to make the case with new evidence or the killer will go free.
ParentalRatingReason: Lightbox Provisional Classification. Official NZ Rating To Be Confirmed.
